channel.title: ASF JIRA
channel.description: This file is an XML representation of an issue

item.title: [HBASE-15475] Allow TimestampsFilter to provide a seek hint
item.description: If a user wants to read specific timestamps currently it's a very linear scan. This is so that all deletes can be respected. However if the user doesn't care about deletes it can dramatically speed up the request to seek.
item.summary: Allow TimestampsFilter to provide a seek hint

status.description: A resolution has been taken, and it is awaiting verification by reporter. From here issues are either reopened, or are closed.
